{"tid":1447020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有警員在太古站將示威者推落扶手電梯","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:50.000Z","uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfd735946c2d3c12005f04d09bff9eb3d9f984a","tid":1447020,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"多名防暴警察及速龍小隊在港鐵太古站C出口的扶手電梯，追捕示威者，期間有防暴警察用警棍向示威者頭部狂打，亦有警員用手捉著示威者，由扶手電梯頂部將示威者推落電梯底部。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事發在晚上的11時許，有示威者嘗試堵塞康山道期間，大批防暴警察趕到，向太古站發放催淚彈，之後突然衝入港鐵站內，有示威者被制服在地上，雙手被綁上帶走，有人頭部受傷，當中包括長者。<br />\n<br />\n有防暴警察查問在港鐵站出口帶口罩的年長女子，期間有市民不斷向警察指罵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474054-20190811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474054-20190811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=8bda6583\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474054-20190811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=49ef1744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474054-20190811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"563daa4c49e3ac0f49ad26f8223b2e5c95752d6e","tid":1447020,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日邊個番工 邊個就係港豬<br />\n全民塞鐵封路, 有狗打狗</span></span>"}]}